   "source": [
    "# SAM 2 Automatic Mask Generation with Ground Truth Tuning\n",
    "\n",
    "Based on your existing notebook, this version adds systematic parameter tuning using ground truth lake data.\n",
    "\n",
    "**Workflow:**\n",
    "1. Load RGB/FCC satellite image OR NDWI image\n",
    "2. Load ground truth lake mask \n",
    "3. Test different SAM 2 parameter combinations\n",
    "4. Find optimal parameters using IoU, precision, and recall metrics\n",
    "5. Apply best configuration to generate final results"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Environment Set-up"
